Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.00,0:00:04.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,《盲点》前情回顾\N{\fs14\b0}Previously on "Blindspot"...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.61,0:00:06.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要跟你说的这件事\N{\fs14\b0}Only three people in the world know{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.12,0:00:07.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世上只有三个人知道\N{\fs14\b0}what I'm about to tell you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.32,0:00:08.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫做白昼计划\N{\fs14\b0}It's called Daylight.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.74,0:00:10.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给简纹身的人是冲着我们来的\N{\fs14\b0}Whoever did this to Jane is coming for us.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.49,0:00:14.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这显而易见  格雷罗必须消失\N{\fs14\b0}It's plain as day, Guerrero needs to disappear.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.16,0:00:18.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些纹身不是用来娱乐的填字游戏\N{\fs14\b0}Those tattoos are not some Sunday morning crossword puzzle.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.08,0:00:22.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里面包含了极为敏感的机密情报\N{\fs14\b0}They contain extremely sensitive classified intelligence.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.36,0:00:24.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你将这件案子  你自己\N{\fs14\b0}You put the case, yourself{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.36,0:00:26.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有一个平民都置于险境\N{\fs14\b0}and a civilian at great risk.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.05,0:00:26.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我疯狂地爱上了你  并且除非是我疯了\N{\fs14\b0}I'm madly in love with you, and unless I'm crazy,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.48,0:00:28.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18\fn方正黑体简体}我想你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.53,0:00:30.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我确信你对我也有相同的感觉\N{\fs14\b0}I'm pretty sure you feel the same way.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.10,0:00:31.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在办我这辈子最大的案件\N{\fs14\b0}I'm working the biggest case of my life.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.61,0:00:33.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以如果你解决了案子  那...\N{\fs14\b0}So, if you solve the case, then...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.81,0:00:35.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\fs14\b0}I'm sorry.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.16,0:00:37.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天晚上和威勒发生的事\N{\fs14\b0}Something happened last night with Weller.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.50,0:00:40.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和威勒探员的关系比较复杂\N{\fs14\b0}Your relationship with Agent Weller is complicated.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.15,0:00:42.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你以前结过婚吗\N{\fs14\b0}Have you ever been married?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.16,0:00:44.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有  我太挑剔\N{\fs14\b0}No, too cheesy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.47,0:00:46.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人圈了一些随机的字母\N{\fs14\b0}Someone circled a bunch of random letters.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.45,0:00:48.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是密码\N{\fs14\b0}It's a secret code.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.25,0:00:52.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人在用这种方式传递信息\N{\fs14\b0}Someone is using this as a communication device.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.57,0:01:06.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死亡原因  颈静脉割伤失血\N{\fs14\b0}Cause of death, exsanguination from laceration to the jugular vein.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.64,0:01:08.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  根据报告\N{\fs14\b0}So, according to the report,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.96,0:01:12.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是用一片玻璃瓶碎片行凶\N{\fs14\b0}she used a piece of glass from a broken bottle.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.27,0:01:14.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暂且不看大卫的案件档案...\N{\fs14\b0}Moving away from David's case file for just a moment...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.76,0:01:16.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她随手找了件东西当凶器\N{\fs14\b0}The fact that she used a found object{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.60,0:01:18.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,表示这不是预谋杀人\N{\fs14\b0}indicates that it wasn't premeditated.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.23,0:01:21.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨晚之后你跟你的家人谈过吗\N{\fs14\b0}Have you spoken to your family since last night?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.65,0:01:24.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只跟我妈谈过  她想过来陪我\N{\fs14\b0}Just my mom. She wanted to fly out{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.21,0:01:26.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我跟她说我没事\N{\fs14\b0}but I told her that I was okay.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.89,0:01:28.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许你该重新考虑一下\N{\fs14\b0}Perhaps you should reconsider?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.64,0:01:30.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个凶手一定受过训练\N{\fs14\b0}The killer had to be trained.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.17,0:01:31.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通常这种情况下\N{\fs14\b0}Normally, agents are asked{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.28,0:01:34.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会要求探员休假\N{\fs14\b0}to take a leave of absence in situations like this.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.12,0:01:36.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有很多证据要去查证\N{\fs14\b0}There is a mountain of evidence that I need to go through.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.80,0:01:39.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要适应突然失去某人是很困难的\N{\fs14\b0}Coming to terms with a sudden loss is complicated,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.74,0:01:41.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尤其是失去爱人\N{\fs14\b0}particularly the loss of a loved one.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.63,0:01:43.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们已经分手了\N{\fs14\b0}We weren't together anymore.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.66,0:01:44.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  也许是这样  但是...\N{\fs14\b0}Well, that may well be the case, but...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.89,0:01:47.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能处理好\N{\fs14\b0}I can handle this.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.06,0:01:51.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会建议让你休假一段时间\N{\fs14\b0}I'm going to recommend you take some time.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.35,0:01:54.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  等等  请不要签字\N{\fs14\b0}No, please... please don't sign that paper.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.54,0:01:59.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能回我的公寓\N{\fs14\b0}I can't go back to my apartment.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.06,0:02:03.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里的每件东西都让我想起他\N{\fs14\b0}Everything there reminds me of him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.47,0:02:08.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的《萤火虫》光碟  我的桌游\N{\fs14\b0}His... "Firefly" DVDs, my board games.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.38,0:02:11.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他没拿走的衣服\N{\fs14\b0}He didn't pick up the last of his clothes{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.99,0:02:13.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得是因为他想...\N{\fs14\b0}I think because he thought...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.84,0:02:15.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帕特森探员  我不能...\N{\fs14\b0}Agent Patterson, I can't just...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.13,0:02:18.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你了  就...\N{\fs14\b0}Please, just...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.97,0:02:20.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我一天时间\N{\fs14\b0}give me one day{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.90,0:02:22.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我在这儿跟队友在一起\N{\fs14\b0}so I can be here with my team,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.89,0:02:25.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我知道我能帮上忙\N{\fs14\b0}because I know that I can help.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.53,0:02:30.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就一天  剩下的事就交给我们\N{\fs14\b0}One day, and then we'll take it from there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.73,0:02:34.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  谢谢你\N{\fs14\b0}Okay. Thank you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.32,0:03:33.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你太过分了\N{\fs14\b0}You are out of control.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.29,0:03:34.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也早啊\N{\fs14\b0}Well, good morning to you, too.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.77,0:03:36.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么能这么鲁莽\N{\fs14\b0}How could you be so reckless?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.98,0:03:38.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你草率的灭口行为\N{\fs14\b0}Guerrero's back in the papers{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.29,0:03:40.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格雷罗的名字又出现在了文件里\N{\fs14\b0}because of your sloppy clean-up job.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.16,0:03:43.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点也不草率\N{\fs14\b0}Oh, there was nothing sloppy about it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.13,0:03:45.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们永远也无法追查到我们身上了\N{\fs14\b0}And they'll never be able to trace it back to us.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.39,0:03:47.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你杀他的时候我就在那栋楼里\N{\fs14\b0}I was in the building when you killed him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.70,0:03:51.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不过是凑巧而已\N{\fs14\b0}That was simply bad timing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.21,0:03:54.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他原本会签署证明的\N{\fs14\b0}He would've signed those papers.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.04,0:03:55.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  现在他不需要了\N{\fs14\b0}Yeah, well, now, he doesn't need to.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.93,0:03:58.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无名氏把我们和白昼计划联系起来\N{\fs14\b0}Jane Doe ties us to Daylight.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.55,0:04:02.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经做了该做的事  现在该你了\N{\fs14\b0}I've done my job. Now, you do yours.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.82,0:04:24.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18\fn方正黑体简体}最后一次机会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.06,0:04:24.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么\N{\fs14\b0}What is that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.80,0:04:28.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是一枚非常敏感的监控设备\N{\fs14\b0}This is a very sensitive surveillance device,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.99,0:04:32.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要你把它放进简的安全屋\N{\fs14\b0}and I want it inside Jane's safe house.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.66,0:04:53.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在这干什么\N{\fs14\b0}What are you doing down here?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.86,0:04:59.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fs14\b0}I don't know.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.41,0:05:04.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想看到这些东西或许能想起什么\N{\fs14\b0}I thought maybe seeing it would trigger something.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.84,0:05:08.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这枚纹身...\N{\fs14\b0}This tattoo...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.73,0:05:10.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简\N{\fs14\b0}Jane.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.34,0:05:11.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不能责怪自己\N{\fs14\b0}You can't blame yourself.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.63,0:05:14.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大卫去图书馆的唯一原因\N{\fs14\b0}The only reason David was in that library{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.47,0:05:16.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是他在追查这个\N{\fs14\b0}was because he was following this.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.28,0:05:17.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我身上布满纹身\N{\fs14\b0}And I'm covered in these,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.96,0:05:20.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可我完全不明白它们代表什么含义\N{\fs14\b0}but I have no control over what they mean{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.11,0:05:22.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者会引发什么事情\N{\fs14\b0}or what happens because of them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.30,0:05:25.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简  这些纹身\N{\fs14\b0}Jane, these tattoos,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.27,0:05:27.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们挽救了许多人的性命\N{\fs14\b0}they've saved a lot of lives.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.04,0:05:28.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次没有\N{\fs14\b0}Not this time.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.34,0:05:33.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次死的既不是恐怖分子也不是罪犯\N{\fs14\b0}This wasn't some terrorist or criminal that died.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.21,0:05:35.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是帕特森的男朋友\N{\fs14\b0}It was Patterson's boyfriend.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.39,0:05:39.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她该怎么从这种伤痛中走出来\N{\fs14\b0}How is she gonna move on from this?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.86,0:05:43.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从来都没有失去过谁\N{\fs14\b0}I've never lost anyone before.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.99,0:05:47.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少记忆中没有\N{\fs14\b0}At least, not anyone I can remember.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.95,0:05:51.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很幸运  走出阴霾需要时间\N{\fs14\b0}You're lucky. It takes time.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.15,0:05:56.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧  该干正事了\N{\fs14\b0}Come on, let's get to work.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.07,0:05:57.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  根据报告内容\N{\fs14\b0}So, according to the report,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.37,0:05:58.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀害大卫的凶手在一本工具书里\N{\fs14\b0}David's killer left some type of encoded message{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.91,0:05:59.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留下了加密信息\N{\fs14\b0}in a reference book.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.77,0:06:02.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  然后她把这张纸再放到\N{\fs14\b0}Yeah, and then she went to a second book and placed{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.63,0:06:04.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二本书的书脊中\N{\fs14\b0}this piece of paper inside the book's spine.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.71,0:06:05.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们怎么知道的\N{\fs14\b0}How do we know this?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.49,0:06:08.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我安排了一个探员监视这本书\N{\fs14\b0}I put an agent in place to surveil the book.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.48,0:06:13.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布洛特探员监视书籍  以防有可疑活动\N{\fs14\b0}Agent Brott was monitoring it for any suspicious activity.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.65,0:06:16.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是他发现了大卫横尸于小巷\N{\fs14\b0}He's the one who found David's body{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.42,0:06:17.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且报告给了我\N{\fs14\b0}in the alley and alerted me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.62,0:06:19.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们收到了指纹识别系统的初步报告\N{\fs14\b0}We got an initial report from IAFIS.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.59,0:06:21.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在书上有枚残缺的指纹\N{\fs14\b0}There was a partial print left in the book.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.50,0:06:23.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们找到指纹了吗\N{\fs14\b0}We have a print?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.51,0:06:30.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你确定你在这没关系吗\N{\fs14\b0}Hey, are you sure that you wanna be here?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.98,0:06:33.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帕特森  别勉强自己  交给我们\N{\fs14\b0}Patterson, it's okay, we got this.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.34,0:06:36.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...  我不会坐视不管的\N{\fs14\b0}I'm... I'm not sitting this one out.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.58,0:06:38.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们找到指纹了吗\N{\fs14\b0}Do we have a print?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.85,0:06:43.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,残缺指纹不是杀害大卫的凶手的\N{\fs14\b0}The partial wasn't from David's killer,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.71,0:06:45.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是一个叫罗杰·列夫金的男子的\N{\fs14\b0}it was from this man named Roger Levkin.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.11,0:06:45.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18\fn方正黑体简体}纽约州  驾照  罗杰·列夫金
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.91,0:06:47.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一位成功的建筑师\N{\fs14\b0}Successful architect,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.36,0:06:50.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住在韦斯切斯特县  无犯罪记录\N{\fs14\b0}lives in Westchester County, clean criminal record.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.72,0:06:53.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与妻子艾米丽已结婚十年\N{\fs14\b0}Married ten years to his wife Emily,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.07,0:06:54.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妻子是纽约大学经济学教授\N{\fs14\b0}an econ professor at NYU.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.80,0:06:56.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这听起来没可疑之处啊\N{\fs14\b0}That doesn't sound very suspicious to me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.62,0:06:58.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了他是在俄罗斯出生的这点\N{\fs14\b0}Except he was born in Russia.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.49,0:07:00.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是靠结婚才成为美国公民的\N{\fs14\b0}Became a U.S. citizen through marriage.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.84,0:07:02.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得他的俄国背景跟案子有关吗\N{\fs14\b0}Do you think his Russian background plays into this?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.00,0:07:06.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,图书馆的书  密码  还有隐藏的信息\N{\fs14\b0}The books in the library, the codes, hidden messages.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.09,0:07:08.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都感觉像俄国的谍报技术\N{\fs14\b0}Feels like Russian tradecraft.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.03,0:07:09.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷战时期的老策略\N{\fs14\b0}Old school Cold War tactics.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.45,0:07:11.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是说我们遇到间谍了吗\N{\fs14\b0}Are you saying we're dealing with spies?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.81,0:07:13.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有一种方法能确定真相\N{\fs14\b0}Well, there's only one way to find out.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.67,0:07:15.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行动吧\N{\fs14\b0}Let's move.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.44,0:07:18.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把图书馆的书分析一下\N{\fs14\b0}I'll put the library books through processing...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.53,0:07:20.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看能不能找到别的加密信息\N{\fs14\b0}see if I can find any codes anywhere.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.42,0:07:21.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs14\b0}Okay.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.61,0:07:38.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你没事吧  -没事  没事\N{\fs14\b0}- Are you okay? - Yeah... yeah.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.50,0:07:40.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看看这个\N{\fs14\b0}Here, take a look at this.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.16,0:07:42.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凶手把这个藏在第二本书里\N{\fs14\b0}Uh, the killer hid that inside the second book.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.63,0:07:44.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是译码器吗\N{\fs14\b0}Some kind of decoding device?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.17,0:07:48.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,47在第一本书里被圈出来\N{\fs14\b0}So 47 was circled in the first book.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.26,0:07:51.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们用两本书肯定是有原因的\N{\fs14\b0}So there must be a reason why they used two books.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.16,0:07:53.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想  可能是指...\N{\fs14\b0}I mean, maybe it's referring to a...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.83,0:07:56.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二本书的页数\N{\fs14\b0}a page in the second book?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.80,0:08:01.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第47页\N{\fs14\b0}So... page 47.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.56,0:08:03.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了\N{\fs14\b0}Here we go.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.15,0:08:06.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加上译码器\N{\fs14\b0}And the decoding device.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.06,0:08:09.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪不得\N{\fs14\b0}Of course.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.48,0:08:12.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把译码器放在书上  看露出的字母\N{\fs14\b0}It's a window box overlay.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.89,0:08:16.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"一切正常  将会继续监视\N{\fs14\b0}"Status nominal. Will continue to monitor.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.13,0:08:18.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无其他消息"\N{\fs14\b0}No further updates."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.12,0:08:19.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她在向上级报告\N{\fs14\b0}She was reporting in.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.15,0:08:22.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在知道这个对我们也没用\N{\fs14\b0}It's useless to us now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.33,0:08:24.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18\fn方正黑体简体}一切正常  将会继续监视  无其他消息
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.44,0:08:39.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不太对劲\N{\fs14\b0}Something's not right.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.42,0:08:43.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们俩  从房子那边包抄\N{\fs14\b0}You two, go around the house that side.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.52,0:08:46.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在后面碰头  塔莎  你守前面\N{\fs14\b0}Meet you around the back. Tasha, cover the front.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.09,0:09:08.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到疑犯的妻子了\N{\fs14\b0}Got eyes on the suspect's wife.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.85,0:09:10.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是人质  被绑在厨房\N{\fs14\b0}She's being held hostage in the kitchen.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.61,0:09:11.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疑犯携带武器\N{\fs14\b0}Suspect is armed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.53,0:09:13.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行动\N{\fs14\b0}Going in.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.46,0:09:23.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\fs14\b0}I'm so sorry.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.94,0:09:25.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴\N{\fs14\b0}Shut up.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.24,0:09:26.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伸出手来\N{\fs14\b0}Give me your hand.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.97,0:09:32.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有另一只手  转过去\N{\fs14\b0}Give me your other hand! Turn over.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.01,0:09:33.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转过去\N{\fs14\b0}Turn over!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.82,0:09:38.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,张开嘴\N{\fs14\b0}Open your mouth.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.84,0:09:40.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,张开嘴\N{\fs14\b0}Open your mouth!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.60,0:09:42.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,张嘴\N{\fs14\b0}Open it!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.75,0:09:49.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他死了\N{\fs14\b0}He's dead.{\r}
