Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.85,0:10:02.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord0\shad0\fn方正兰亭粗黑_GBK\fs18\c&HE1D9D6&\alpha10\fad(530,0)\t(23,2736,\fscx110\fscy110)\b0\pos(187,156)}第一季  第十集
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.65,0:10:09.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要见我\N{\fs14\b0}You wanted to see me?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.33,0:10:12.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么样了\N{\fs14\b0}How are you doing?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.60,0:10:14.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还好\N{\fs14\b0}Fine.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.38,0:10:16.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你才不好\N{\fs14\b0}You're not fine.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.06,0:10:18.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托  别让我回家\N{\fs14\b0}Please, don't send me home.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.96,0:10:24.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着  我知道失去某人是什么感觉\N{\fs14\b0}Look... I know what it's like to lose someone.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.13,0:10:27.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也知道你有多想找到答案\N{\fs14\b0}And I know what it's like to need answers.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.25,0:10:30.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但一旦你觉得这一切难以承受\N{\fs14\b0}But if at any point this gets too difficult for you,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.91,0:10:33.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你得跟我说实话\N{\fs14\b0}you have to be honest with me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.81,0:10:46.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们会做毒性检测\N{\fs14\b0}They're gonna run a tox screen,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.92,0:10:48.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但罗杰看起来是死于\N{\fs14\b0}but it looks like Roger died{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.07,0:10:50.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,速效毒药  很可能是氰化物\N{\fs14\b0}from a fast-acting poison, probably cyanide.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.50,0:10:51.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点说不通\N{\fs14\b0}Something doesn't add up.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.46,0:10:53.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果罗杰真的是俄国间谍\N{\fs14\b0}If Roger really was a Russian spy{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.02,0:10:55.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的美国妻子是他的掩护\N{\fs14\b0}and his American wife was his cover,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.99,0:10:57.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那他为什么想要杀她\N{\fs14\b0}why would he try to kill her?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.12,0:10:58.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们伪装得很完美\N{\fs14\b0}They had the perfect setup--{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.13,0:10:59.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,温馨的家庭  体面的工作\N{\fs14\b0}nice home, good jobs.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.48,0:11:01.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道  在谎言里生活十年太长了\N{\fs14\b0}I don't know, ten years is a long time to live a lie.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.49,0:11:03.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能他崩溃了\N{\fs14\b0}Maybe he just snapped.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.06,0:11:05.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这跟那些图书馆的书肯定有联系\N{\fs14\b0}There's gotta be a connection to those library books.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.09,0:11:06.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟它们接触过的两个人\N{\fs14\b0}It's too big of a coincidence that two people{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.58,0:11:09.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在24小时内都死了  这也太巧合了\N{\fs14\b0}who had contact with him end up dead within 24 hours.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.46,0:11:10.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认为这一切\N{\fs14\b0}You think David finding those books{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.86,0:11:12.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟大卫找到那些书有关吗\N{\fs14\b0}has something to do with all of this?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.68,0:11:15.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗杰的妻子根本不知道他今早为什么性情大变\N{\fs14\b0}Roger's wife has no idea what made him turn this morning.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.03,0:11:15.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他曾提到过\N{\fs14\b0}He mentioned something about{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.87,0:11:17.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到会爱上她\N{\fs14\b0}never meaning to fall in love with her.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.96,0:11:19.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他还说什么了吗\N{\fs14\b0}Did he say anything else?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.19,0:11:20.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她说他还提到了目标\N{\fs14\b0}She said that he was talking about targets{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.94,0:11:21.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有一个行动\N{\fs14\b0}and an operation.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.89,0:11:22.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听起来不妙\N{\fs14\b0}That's not good.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.81,0:11:23.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看这个\N{\fs14\b0}Check this out.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.84,0:11:26.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这跟图书馆监控照片里的女士是同一个人\N{\fs14\b0}The same lady from the library surveillance photo.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.50,0:11:30.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相同身材  相同年龄  再看她的头发\N{\fs14\b0}Same build, same age, and look at the hair.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.29,0:11:32.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得是她杀了大卫吗\N{\fs14\b0}Do you think she could be David's killer?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.71,0:11:37.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是凯特·威廉姆斯\N{\fs14\b0}This is Kate Williams.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.51,0:11:40.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是我们的朋友  怎么了\N{\fs14\b0}She's a friend. Why?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.83,0:11:44.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯特·威廉姆斯是布朗克斯区的五年级老师\N{\fs14\b0}Kate Williams is a fifth grade teacher in the Bronx.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.37,0:11:47.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住在公园大道和麦迪逊大道间的东77大街上\N{\fs14\b0}She lives on 77th between Park and Madison.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.35,0:11:49.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做老师的住得起这么好的地段吗\N{\fs14\b0}Fancy address on a teacher's salary?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.38,0:11:51.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她丈夫是一个商业地产经纪\N{\fs14\b0}Her husband is a commercial real estate broker,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.70,0:11:53.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,内森·威廉姆斯\N{\fs14\b0}Nathan Williams.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.28,0:11:55.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结婚十年  没有孩子\N{\fs14\b0}Married ten years, no kids.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.35,0:11:57.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯特跟俄国有什么关系吗\N{\fs14\b0}Does Kate have any connections to Russia?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.52,0:11:59.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有  关系还不小  她在那出生\N{\fs14\b0}Yeah, a big one. She was born there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.70,0:12:00.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她符合我们对\N{\fs14\b0}She matches the description{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.90,0:12:03.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀死大卫的凶手的描述和侧写\N{\fs14\b0}and the profile of David's killer.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.16,0:12:04.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是她\N{\fs14\b0}It has to be her.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.94,0:12:08.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当发现凯特没有回家之后\N{\fs14\b0}Nathan filed a missing persons report with the NYPD{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.36,0:12:10.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,内森向纽约警察局报了案\N{\fs14\b0}when Kate didn't come home.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.24,0:12:11.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他现在正在布鲁克林的第82分局\N{\fs14\b0}He's at the 82nd precinct in Brooklyn{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.92,0:12:13.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接受盘问\N{\fs14\b0}right now being questioned.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.39,0:12:14.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他们把他留在那\N{\fs14\b0}Tell 'em to hold him there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.61,0:12:15.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得跟他谈谈\N{\fs14\b0}We need to talk to him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.91,0:12:18.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是卡拉·斯隆探员\N{\fs14\b0}This is Agent Kara Sloane{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.44,0:12:20.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来自反间谍司\N{\fs14\b0}with the Counter Espionage Division.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.85,0:12:22.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她会协助我们\N{\fs14\b0}She's going to be assisting us.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.46,0:12:24.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅菲尔助理局长跟我说了具体情况\N{\fs14\b0}Assistant Director Mayfair got me up to speed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.62,0:12:26.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些新发现跟我们\N{\fs14\b0}These new developments are lining up{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.18,0:12:27.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接到的可能有卧底的\N{\fs14\b0}with chatter that we've been hearing{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.32,0:12:28.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情报相符\N{\fs14\b0}about a possible sleeper cell.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.88,0:12:30.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯特·威廉姆斯绝对符合他们的作案手法\N{\fs14\b0}Kate Williams certainly fits the MO.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.99,0:12:34.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出生在俄国  跟成功的美国人结婚\N{\fs14\b0}Russian born, married to a successful American citizen,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.10,0:12:36.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全融入美国\N{\fs14\b0}fully assimilated into the community,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.04,0:12:38.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在此之前一直过着看似平凡的生活\N{\fs14\b0}up until now, leading a seemingly normal life.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.39,0:12:42.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大卫被杀和罗杰·列夫金自杀\N{\fs14\b0}With David's murder and Roger Levkin's suicide,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.39,0:12:44.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都指向了某种行动\N{\fs14\b0}it all points to some sort of mission.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.33,0:12:45.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在俄国大使馆的线人\N{\fs14\b0}My source at the Russian Embassy{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.62,0:12:48.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,称那里的气氛在12小时前变得紧张了\N{\fs14\b0}says that things started to heat up about 12 hours ago.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.23,0:12:49.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多是大卫被杀的时候\N{\fs14\b0}Around the same time David got killed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.50,0:12:51.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能俄国人以为大卫是联调局的\N{\fs14\b0}Well, maybe the Russians thought David was a Fed{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.46,0:12:52.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们被盯上了\N{\fs14\b0}and was onto them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.26,0:12:54.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可能会刺激他们采取行动\N{\fs14\b0}Which could have activated their mission.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.42,0:12:56.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗杰也提到了目标之类的\N{\fs14\b0}Roger did mention something about targets.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.35,0:12:59.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们所有的情报都指向暗杀行动\N{\fs14\b0}All of our intel points to assassination plots,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.11,0:13:00.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是目标是谁  原因是什么还不清楚\N{\fs14\b0}but who or why are big unknowns.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.97,0:13:04.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗杰·列夫金攻击了他的妻子\N{\fs14\b0}Roger Levkin's mark was his wife.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.40,0:13:07.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,间谍们的目标会不会是他们的配偶呢\N{\fs14\b0}Could the spies be targeting their spouses?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.04,0:13:09.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有可能  或者她是例外\N{\fs14\b0}Possibly, or she could have been the anomaly.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.56,0:13:11.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们实在没有足够的信息\N{\fs14\b0}We simply don't have enough information.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.03,0:13:12.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简和我去布鲁克林\N{\fs14\b0}Jane and I'll head to Brooklyn.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.75,0:13:14.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,审问凯特的丈夫\N{\fs14\b0}We'll interview Kate's husband.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.42,0:13:16.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们俩  去上东区\N{\fs14\b0}You two, head to the Upper East Side,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.65,0:13:19.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿到地址  看看在房子里能找到什么\N{\fs14\b0}get that address and see what you can find at that house.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.30,0:13:22.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18\fn方正黑体简体}第82分局
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.82,0:13:24.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她昨天下班没有回家\N{\fs14\b0}When she didn't come home from work yesterday,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.06,0:13:25.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就报警了\N{\fs14\b0}I called the police.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.10,0:13:26.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她之前失踪过吗\N{\fs14\b0}Has she gone missing before?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.39,0:13:27.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有  从来没有\N{\fs14\b0}No, never.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.24,0:13:29.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打给了她所有的朋友  没有人跟她联系过\N{\fs14\b0}I've called all her friends, no one's heard from her.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.72,0:13:31.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你妻子出生在俄国\N{\fs14\b0}Your wife was born in Russia.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.47,0:13:33.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她和那边的家人还有联系吗\N{\fs14\b0}Has she stayed in contact with her family back there?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.00,0:13:35.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯特小时候就失去了双亲\N{\fs14\b0}Kate lost her parents when she was a child.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.90,0:13:37.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那她在纽约有没有俄国的朋友\N{\fs14\b0}What about any Russian friends in New York?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.56,0:13:38.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟他们有联系吗\N{\fs14\b0}Ties to the community?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.71,0:13:40.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗杰·列夫金应该算\N{\fs14\b0}I guess, Roger Levkin,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.12,0:13:41.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但凯特和他妻子是朋友\N{\fs14\b0}but Kate's friend with his wife.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.61,0:13:43.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们问这个做什么\N{\fs14\b0}What does this have to do with anything?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.07,0:13:45.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要从各个角度进行调查  先生\N{\fs14\b0}We're investigating every angle right now, sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.54,0:13:47.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你收到她的消息请联系我们\N{\fs14\b0}Let us know if you do hear from her, and...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.73,0:13:50.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有消息也会通知你\N{\fs14\b0}we'll do the same if we hear anything.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.74,0:13:54.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帕特森\N{\fs14\b0}Patterson?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.01,0:13:55.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了我还有斯隆探员\N{\fs14\b0}Actually, it's me and Agent Sloane.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.55,0:13:56.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有什么发现\N{\fs14\b0}What have you got?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.98,0:13:58.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一直在调查间谍嫌疑人\N{\fs14\b0}We've been drilling down into the lives{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.31,0:14:00.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及他们配偶的生活情况\N{\fs14\b0}of our suspected spies and their spouses.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.57,0:14:03.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们交叉比对了车管所的记录\N{\fs14\b0}Our vector search cross-checked DMV records,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.47,0:14:04.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,社交媒体主页\N{\fs14\b0}social media pages,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.98,0:14:06.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信用卡账单等等所有方面\N{\fs14\b0}credit card receipts, you name it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.27,0:14:08.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发现他们都与一个人有关联\N{\fs14\b0}Turns out there's one common denominator.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.49,0:14:09.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥利维亚·戴利迪奥\N{\fs14\b0}Olivia Delidio.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.80,0:14:11.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这就把她的照片发给你\N{\fs14\b0}I'm sending you her photo now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.99,0:14:14.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们查到她什么信息了\N{\fs14\b0}So what do you got on her?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.88,0:14:17.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生于俄罗斯  与一名美国人结婚12年\N{\fs14\b0}Russian born, married to an American for 12 years.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.51,0:14:20.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不是普通美国人  而是爱德华·戴利迪奥\N{\fs14\b0}And not just any American. Edward Delidio.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.66,0:14:22.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,《纽约时报》的编辑\N{\fs14\b0}An editor of "The New York Times."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.57,0:14:23.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们有两个年幼的孩子\N{\fs14\b0}They have two young children{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.53,0:14:24.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住在葛莱美西公园\N{\fs14\b0}and they live in Gramercy Park.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.88,0:14:26.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帕特森  派一支小队去找她丈夫\N{\fs14\b0}Patterson, send a team to the husband--{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.78,0:14:27.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他可能会成为目标\N{\fs14\b0}he could be a target.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.70,0:14:28.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就办\N{\fs14\b0}Yeah, on it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.00,0:14:30.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥利维亚的情况也很符合\N{\fs14\b0}Olivia seems to fit the mold,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.30,0:14:32.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嫁了一个成功且能获取消息的丈夫\N{\fs14\b0}marrying a successful and connected spouse.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.37,0:14:34.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有奥利维亚的地址吗\N{\fs14\b0}Got an address for Olivia?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.11,0:14:36.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她在皇后博物馆工作\N{\fs14\b0}She works at Queens Museum.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.64,0:14:40.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,俄国人怎么如此确定他们的特工\N{\fs14\b0}How could the Russians be so sure their agents{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.02,0:14:41.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能让这些人娶她们\N{\fs14\b0}could get these people to marry them?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.92,0:14:44.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们肯定分析了这些目标很多年\N{\fs14\b0}I'm sure they profiled their targets for years,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.41,0:14:47.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据他们的人格  兴趣创造了完美的妻子\N{\fs14\b0}creating matches based on personalities, interests.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.87,0:14:50.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-这得下很大功夫  -但也值得\N{\fs14\b0}- That's a lot of effort. - It's worth it for them.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.33,0:14:53.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能与美国人同化就不会被抓\N{\fs14\b0}Being able to assimilate so they prevent getting caught.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.05,0:14:57.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但就这样完全放弃了自己的生活\N{\fs14\b0}But still, to just give up your whole life like that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.95,0:15:01.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想知道她们有没有后悔过\N{\fs14\b0}I wonder if they ever regretted it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.36,0:15:06.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18\fn方正黑体简体}皇后博物馆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.81,0:15:09.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  女士\N{\fs14\b0}Hi, ma'am.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.83,0:15:12.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联调局的  我们想找奥利维亚·戴利迪奥\N{\fs14\b0}We're the FBI, we're looking for Olivia Delidio.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.71,0:15:14.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她在纽约全景图那里\N{\fs14\b0}She's in the Panorama.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.28,0:15:15.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs14\b0}Thank you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.33,0:15:26.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生  我叫科特·威勒\N{\fs14\b0}Sir? My name is Kurt Weller.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.09,0:15:27.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是联调局的\N{\fs14\b0}I'm with the FBI.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.31,0:15:30.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在找奥利维亚·戴利迪奥\N{\fs14\b0}I'm looking for Olivia Delidio.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.28,0:15:32.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她在那里\N{\fs14\b0}That's her... over there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.49,0:15:35.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是她吗  谢谢\N{\fs14\b0}That's her? Thank you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.48,0:15:41.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她要逃跑\N{\fs14\b0}She's running!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.78,0:15:52.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18\fn方正黑体简体}皇后博物馆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.98,0:16:10.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是联调局的  我需要借用你的摩托车\N{\fs14\b0}I'm with the FBI, I need to borrow your bike.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.75,0:16:38.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下车\N{\fs14\b0}Get out of the car!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.66,0:16:42.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出来\N{\fs14\b0}Out.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.59,0:16:50.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\fn方正兰亭黑_GBK\fs18\b0\pos(191,227)\c&HCAA9C2&}430被抓了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.47,0:16:52.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\fn方正兰亭黑_GBK\fs18\b0\pos(191,227)\c&HCAA9C2&}立即除掉你们俩的目标
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.53,0:16:54.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\fn方正兰亭黑_GBK\fs18\b0\pos(191,227)\c&HCAA9C2&}情报传递点已经给你留了包裹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.14,0:16:56.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\fn方正兰亭黑_GBK\fs18\b0\pos(191,227)\c&HCAA9C2&}明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.91,0:17:00.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么要跑\N{\fs14\b0}Why did you run?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.60,0:17:02.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯特·威廉姆斯在哪\N{\fs14\b0}Where is Kate Williams?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.12,0:17:04.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她一点都不紧张\N{\fs14\b0}She doesn't even seem nervous.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.67,0:17:06.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她受苏联训练多年\N{\fs14\b0}She's had years of Soviet training.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.97,0:17:08.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,查过她嘴里有没有氰化物了吗\N{\fs14\b0}Has she been checked for a cyanide cap?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.84,0:17:10.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,查过了  她没藏毒\N{\fs14\b0}Yeah, we checked her, she's clean.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.43,0:17:12.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最后问你一次\N{\fs14\b0}This is the last time that I'm gonna ask you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.28,0:17:13.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯特·威廉姆斯在哪\N{\fs14\b0}Where is Kate Williams?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.43,0:17:15.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过了  不知道\N{\fs14\b0}I told you, I don't know.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.10,0:17:16.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们去过你的公寓了\N{\fs14\b0}We were at your apartment.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.37,0:17:18.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,门卫证实了凯特昨晚睡在那里\N{\fs14\b0}Your doorman confirmed Kate slept there last night.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.91,0:17:21.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道你在说什么\N{\fs14\b0}I have no idea what you're talking about.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.26,0:17:24.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  我和凯特都是俄罗斯人\N{\fs14\b0}Yes, Kate and I are both Russian.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.73,0:17:26.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都嫁给了美国人\N{\fs14\b0}We both married Americans.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.28,0:17:30.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是好朋友  时常联系\N{\fs14\b0}We're good friends, we talk all the time.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.37,0:17:31.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"时常联系"\N{\fs14\b0}"We talk all the time."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.63,0:17:34.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们怎么就成了间谍\N{\fs14\b0}How does that make us spies?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.07,0:17:35.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这个\N{\fs14\b0}That's it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.46,0:17:37.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么\N{\fs14\b0}What's it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.61,0:17:40.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帕特森  是什么\N{\fs14\b0}Patterson, what's it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.52,0:17:47.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这是政治迫害\N{\fs14\b0}This is a witch hunt!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.46,0:17:49.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的律师和丈夫在哪\N{\fs14\b0}Where's my lawyer and my husband?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.13,0:17:50.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们通知了你丈夫  他正带着律师赶来\N{\fs14\b0}We spoke to your husband, he's bringing your lawyer.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.87,0:17:52.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与此同时  你也可以说出实情\N{\fs14\b0}In the meantime, you can help yourself out{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.42,0:17:54.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮助你自己\N{\fs14\b0}by telling us the truth.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.81,0:17:58.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉打断\N{\fs14\b0}Sorry to interrupt.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.68,0:17:59.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事  能出去说吗\N{\fs14\b0}It's okay. You wanna talk outside?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.64,0:18:02.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有个发现  给我一分钟\N{\fs14\b0}I have something, I just need a minute.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.43,0:18:08.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认得这个吗\N{\fs14\b0}Do you recognize this?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.63,0:18:09.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是本书\N{\fs14\b0}It's a book.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.84,0:18:15.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你和你朋友凯特的通讯工具\N{\fs14\b0}This was used as a communication device by you and your friend Kate.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.45,0:18:17.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在监控录像里看到\N{\fs14\b0}We have video surveillance of her{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.08,0:18:19.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨晚她曾去过布鲁克林历史协会\N{\fs14\b0}at the Brooklyn Historical Society last night.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.47,0:18:21.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没去过那儿\N{\fs14\b0}I've never been there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.45,0:18:24.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是一本贴有归还日期卡的工具书\N{\fs14\b0}This is a reference book with a due date card,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.46,0:18:25.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这点不合乎常理\N{\fs14\b0}which doesn't really make any sense{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.00,0:18:29.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为工具书是无法外借的\N{\fs14\b0}because reference books can't be checked out.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.34,0:18:31.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以这些日期  不是真的日期\N{\fs14\b0}So, these dates... these aren't really dates.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.85,0:18:33.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吗\N{\fs14\b0}Are they?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.15,0:18:38.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,\N{\fs14\b0}523  207  430\N523, 207, 430.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.82,0:18:43.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,分别是三名间谍的代号\N{\fs14\b0}Three code names for three spies.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.45,0:18:47.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗杰  凯特  还有你\N{\fs14\b0}Roger, Kate, and you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.04,0:18:49.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想象力真丰富\N{\fs14\b0}That is a wild guess.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.07,0:18:51.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者我根本没猜错\N{\fs14\b0}Or not a guess at all.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.15,0:18:55.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做了笔迹分析  结果完全匹配\N{\fs14\b0}I ran a handwriting analysis and it's a perfect match.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.76,0:18:57.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她在诈她\N{\fs14\b0}She's bluffing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.07,0:18:59.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她根本没时间去做分析测试\N{\fs14\b0}She couldn't have had time to run that test.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.49,0:19:04.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外...我们还发现了一枚残缺的指纹\N{\fs14\b0}That... and we found a partial print,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.12,0:19:06.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以确认你是其中一名通讯人\N{\fs14\b0}which confirms that you're part of the ring.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.60,0:19:07.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不可能找到指纹\N{\fs14\b0}There's no way you have a print.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.72,0:19:10.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从来都没见过这本书\N{\fs14\b0}I-I've never seen that book before.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.58,0:19:17.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们好像没找到奥利维亚的指纹吧\N{\fs14\b0}I didn't think we had a print for Olivia.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.55,0:19:20.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  那是罗杰的\N{\fs14\b0}We don't. That's Roger's.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.77,0:19:24.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你大意了\N{\fs14\b0}You got complacent.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.35,0:19:26.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟十年了\N{\fs14\b0}Ten years.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.25,0:19:30.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不好  也许你忘记擦掉书上的指纹了\N{\fs14\b0}I don't know, maybe you just forgot to wipe the book down.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.12,0:19:33.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你无路可走了\N{\fs14\b0}You're out of moves.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.75,0:19:37.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你拖得时间越久\N{\fs14\b0}The longer you let this drag out,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.67,0:19:39.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距离和你孩子相见的时间就越久\N{\fs14\b0}the longer it's gonna be before you see your children.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.85,0:19:41.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不关我孩子的事\N{\fs14\b0}My children have done nothing wrong.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.50,0:19:43.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  他们是无辜的  但你不是\N{\fs14\b0}You're right, they're innocent, but you're not.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.94,0:19:45.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会被指控间谍罪\N{\fs14\b0}You'll be charged with espionage,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.29,0:19:47.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叛国罪  谋杀从犯\N{\fs14\b0}treason, accessory to murder,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.32,0:19:50.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸运的话  也要在牢里待上一辈子\N{\fs14\b0}thrown in prison for the rest of your life, if you're lucky.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.88,0:19:55.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥利维亚\N{\fs14\b0}Olivia...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.36,0:19:58.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该怎么做你自己决定\N{\fs14\b0}it's up to you how this plays out.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.76,0:20:00.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你还想看着自己的孩子长大\N{\fs14\b0}If you wanna see your children grow up,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.71,0:20:02.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老实交代吧\N{\fs14\b0}start talking.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.70,0:20:10.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我十几岁时就被招入了\N{\fs14\b0}I was recruited as a teenager.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.35,0:20:14.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们说我要在美国参与一项长期任务\N{\fs14\b0}They said I would be part of a long-term mission in America.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.36,0:20:15.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的任务是什么\N{\fs14\b0}And what was your mission?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.00,0:20:17.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嫁给一位美国目标\N{\fs14\b0}To marry an American target{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.50,0:20:19.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他能接触到一些\N{\fs14\b0}who had access to the kind of information{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.06,0:20:20.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能令俄罗斯感兴趣的情报\N{\fs14\b0}that could be interesting to Russia.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.49,0:20:22.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么情报\N{\fs14\b0}What kind of information?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.44,0:20:28.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,《纽约时报》刊登的那些人的机密报告\N{\fs14\b0}Confidential reports on people profiled in "The New York Times."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.92,0:20:31.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我用我丈夫的密码登录了他的账号\N{\fs14\b0}I used my husband's passwords to get into his account.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.41,0:20:33.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后你用那本工具书把情报传回去\N{\fs14\b0}And you used the reference book to communicate the intel back?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.73,0:20:35.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要知道  我是个孤儿\N{\fs14\b0}You have to understand, I was an orphan,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.54,0:20:36.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没饭吃\N{\fs14\b0}I was starving.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.49,0:20:40.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有住处  我什么都没有\N{\fs14\b0}I had nowhere to sleep, I-I had nothing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.20,0:20:41.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无人寄托\N{\fs14\b0}No one.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.92,0:20:44.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才答应这么做\N{\fs14\b0}That's why I agreed to do this.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.63,0:20:47.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有机会过上普通人的生活\N{\fs14\b0}Have a chance at a normal life.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.60,0:20:50.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没想到会爱上爱德华\N{\fs14\b0}I never expected to fall in love with Edward.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.26,0:20:52.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后又有了孩子\N{\fs14\b0}And then we had children.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.83,0:20:56.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一切看起来就像命中注定\N{\fs14\b0}And it all seemed like it was meant to be.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.93,0:21:00.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,送回情报只是微不足道的代价\N{\fs14\b0}Sending the intel back was a small price to pay.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.96,0:21:03.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们没伤害过任何人\N{\fs14\b0}We never hurt anyone.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.31,0:21:04.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在有了\N{\fs14\b0}Until now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.80,0:21:07.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个无辜人\N{\fs14\b0}An innocent man{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.73,0:21:11.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你们的行动而死\N{\fs14\b0}is dead because of your actions!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.70,0:21:14.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得这只是个微不足道的代价吗\N{\fs14\b0}Do you think that that is a small price to pay?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.45,0:21:16.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帕特森  过来\N{\fs14\b0}Patterson, come here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.64,0:21:23.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你理解你很气愤\N{\fs14\b0}You have every reason to be angry.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.92,0:21:25.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大卫是你非常在乎的人\N{\fs14\b0}David was someone that you really cared about,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.94,0:21:28.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以这是我们大家的事\N{\fs14\b0}so that matters to all of us.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.51,0:21:31.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会抓到凯特的\N{\fs14\b0}We will get Kate.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.03,0:21:33.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我保证\N{\fs14\b0}I promise you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.92,0:21:37.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在必须坦白一切\N{\fs14\b0}You need to tell us everything now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.82,0:21:41.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,图书馆那本书暴露后发生了什么\N{\fs14\b0}What happened after the library book was exposed?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.92,0:21:44.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经说太多了\N{\fs14\b0}I've already said too much.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.29,0:21:49.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"上帝  救救我吧"\N{\fs14\b0}"God help me."{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.26,0:21:51.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毫无意外  你会说俄语\N{\fs14\b0}Of course, you speak Russian.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.64,0:21:53.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我试试\N{\fs14\b0}Let me try.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.02,0:21:55.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以让她敞开心扉\N{\fs14\b0}I can get her to open up.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.47,0:21:57.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行\N{\fs14\b0}Yeah.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.07,0:22:02.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\fn方正兰亭黑_GBK\fs18\b0\pos(191,227)\c&H6AE9D0&}让我帮你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.36,0:22:09.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\fn方正兰亭黑_GBK\fs18\b0\pos(191,227)\c&H6AE9D0&}我知道孤独害怕的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.08,0:22:12.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\fn方正兰亭黑_GBK\fs18\b0\pos(191,227)\c&H6AE9D0&}我也是个孤儿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.37,0:22:15.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\bord0\shad0\fn方正兰亭黑_GBK\fs18\b0\pos(191,227)\c&H6AE9D0&}最不幸的事莫过于无家可归
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.94,0:22:20.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你爱你的孩子\N{\fs14\b0}I know you love your children,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.56,0:22:21.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们对你而言\N{\fs14\b0}and they mean more than any promise{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.85,0:22:23.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比你答应过俄国的任何事都要重要\N{\fs14\b0}you could have made to Russia.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.28,0:22:27.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子就是我的全部\N{\fs14\b0}My... children are my world.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.54,0:22:29.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就做正确的选择\N{\fs14\b0}Then do the right thing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.06,0:22:31.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都告诉我们\N{\fs14\b0}Tell us everything.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.16,0:22:33.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你收到了什么命令\N{\fs14\b0}What are your orders?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.18,0:22:37.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的联络人昨晚启动了撤离计划\N{\fs14\b0}Our handler initiated the extraction plan last night.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.56,0:22:39.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们收到了目标\N{\fs14\b0}We were given... targets.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.95,0:22:41.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暗杀目标\N{\fs14\b0}People to kill.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.16,0:22:42.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,期限\N{\fs14\b0}Timeline?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.10,0:22:46.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,24小时\N{\fs14\b0}24 hours.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.18,0:22:47.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的目标是谁\N{\fs14\b0}Who's your target?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.51,0:22:49.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲍里斯·伊万诺维奇\N{\fs14\b0}Boris Ivanovich,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.22,0:22:50.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,《纽约时报》的记者\N{\fs14\b0}a journalist at the "Times".{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.98,0:22:52.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是你的联络人发现你被捕了\N{\fs14\b0}What happens to Boris once your handlers{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.64,0:22:54.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲍里斯会怎么样\N{\fs14\b0}find out you were captured?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.33,0:22:56.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会有其他特工完成任务\N{\fs14\b0}Another operative completes the mission.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.82,0:22:59.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我给你们发了\N{\fs14\b0}I'm sending you a photo{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.71,0:23:02.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目标人鲍里斯·伊万诺维奇的照片\N{\fs14\b0}of the target, Boris Ivanovich.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.17,0:23:02.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18\fn方正黑体简体}鲍里斯·伊万诺维奇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.38,0:23:04.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他两年前叛逃到了美国\N{\fs14\b0}He defected to the States two years ago.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.18,0:23:06.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之前  他是反普京博客的博主\N{\fs14\b0}Prior to that, he was an anti-Putin blogger{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.18,0:23:07.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有很多粉丝\N{\fs14\b0}with a huge following.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.90,0:23:09.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上百万俄国人上他的网站看新闻\N{\fs14\b0}I mean, millions of Russians get their news from his site.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.00,0:23:10.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你警告鲍里斯了吗\N{\fs14\b0}Did you alert Boris?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.90,0:23:12.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的电话转接语音邮箱了\N{\fs14\b0}His phone goes straight to voicemail.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.43,0:23:14.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我黑进了他的邮箱账号\N{\fs14\b0}But I was able to hack into his email account,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.95,0:23:16.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎他准备去柯立芝公园\N{\fs14\b0}and it looks like he's supposed to meet up{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.37,0:23:19.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,见一位爆料人\N{\fs14\b0}with a source for a tip in Coolidge Park.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.05,0:23:20.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桥附近的公园长椅\N{\fs14\b0}Park bench by the bridge.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.38,0:23:27.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲍里斯\N{\fs14\b0}Boris.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.11,0:23:32.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他死了\N{\fs14\b0}He's dead.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.85,0:23:43.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥利维亚证实了确实有三名特工\N{\fs14\b0}Olivia confirmed there were three operatives.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.10,0:23:44.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每人都有各自的目标\N{\fs14\b0}Each had a separate target.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.31,0:23:46.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么还剩一个身份不明\N{\fs14\b0}So that leaves one sitting duck.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.11,0:23:48.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的人在分析埃米莉和鲍里斯的特征\N{\fs14\b0}My teams have been profiling Emily and Boris,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.12,0:23:49.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望能发现什么线索\N{\fs14\b0}hoping it'll give us some clues{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.43,0:23:50.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找出最后一位目标的身份\N{\fs14\b0}to the final target's identity.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.95,0:23:52.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了教授的身份之外\N{\fs14\b0}In addition to being a professor,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.26,0:23:52.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18\fn方正黑体简体}埃米莉·勒夫金\N克里姆林宫的梦魇吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.51,0:23:55.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,埃米莉·勒夫金出席过几次国会听证会\N{\fs14\b0}Emily Levkin testified at several congressional hearings.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.62,0:23:59.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她支持就侵犯人权及兼并克里米亚问题\N{\fs14\b0}She was in favor for sanctioning Russia for human rights violations{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.38,0:24:01.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,制裁俄罗斯\N{\fs14\b0}and its annexation of Crimea.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.89,0:24:05.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲍里斯·伊万诺维奇因博客和专栏闻名\N{\fs14\b0}Boris Ivanovich was known for his blog and op-ed pieces{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.71,0:24:07.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,揭露了普京政府的腐败\N{\fs14\b0}exposing Putin's corruption.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.25,0:24:09.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以二者都是直言批判俄国政治的人\N{\fs14\b0}So both were vocal critics of Russia's policies.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.58,0:24:11.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这对统治阶级可不是什么好事\N{\fs14\b0}That could be bad news for the ruling class.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.46,0:24:14.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普京一直镇压着他认为不爱国的人民\N{\fs14\b0}Putin's been cracking down on people he deems unpatriotic.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.20,0:24:16.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就能解释他派这些潜伏特工\N{\fs14\b0}So, it makes sense that he'd use these sleeper agents{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.21,0:24:17.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来除掉在美国的反对者了\N{\fs14\b0}to take down dissenters in the United States.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.91,0:24:20.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可还是无法缩小多少范围\N{\fs14\b0}That still doesn't narrow it down much.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.60,0:24:23.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最好的办法还是找到凯特·威廉姆斯\N{\fs14\b0}Our best bet is to find Kate Williams.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.75,0:24:44.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有凯特的线索吗\N{\fs14\b0}Any leads on Kate?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.06,0:24:47.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有  但我发现奥利维亚和罗杰\N{\fs14\b0}Not exactly, but I discovered both Olivia and Roger{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.28,0:24:48.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都上过同一个网站\N{\fs14\b0}started checking the same website{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.88,0:24:51.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在大卫...\N{\fs14\b0}last night after David...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.79,0:24:54.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在书被发现的前一晚\N{\fs14\b0}after the book was compromised.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.83,0:24:55.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18\fn方正黑体简体}布莱顿沙滩
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.29,0:24:56.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布莱顿沙滩旅游局\N{\fs14\b0}Brighton Beach Tourism Board.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.40,0:24:58.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布莱顿沙滩  那简直是小敖德萨{\fs14}[俄国城市]{\c}\N{\fs14\b0}Brighton Beach? That's Little Odessa.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.07,0:25:00.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很多俄罗斯人住在那里\N{\fs14\b0}There's a huge Russian community there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.31,0:25:02.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直没找到除此之外的联系\N{\fs14\b0}I couldn't figure out the connection beyond that{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.91,0:25:05.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到我拿到了罗杰的毒理检验报告\N{\fs14\b0}until I got Roger's tox screen back.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.56,0:25:07.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以为他死于氰化物中毒\N{\fs14\b0}I thought he died from cyanide poisoning.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.40,0:25:08.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实是死于另一种毒药\N{\fs14\b0}The actual C.O.D. was from a poison{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.00,0:25:11.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫"乌头"  一种致命花卉\N{\fs14\b0}called aconite... deadly flowering plant.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.02,0:25:12.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那和这个网站有什么关系\N{\fs14\b0}So what has that got to do with this website?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.97,0:25:15.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看实时网络摄像\N{\fs14\b0}Check out the live webcam.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.49,0:25:18.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,360度景象  覆盖所有餐厅和商店\N{\fs14\b0}360-degree view of all the restaurants and shops,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.88,0:25:20.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其中有家花店\N{\fs14\b0}including a flower shop.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.29,0:25:21.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得乌头是从这来的吗\N{\fs14\b0}You think that's where the aconite came from?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.60,0:25:24.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信肯定和这些间谍有关\N{\fs14\b0}Pretty sure there's a connection to our spies.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.05,0:25:27.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看这橱窗陈设\N{\fs14\b0}Check out the window display.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.22,0:25:29.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些花环的价格很奇怪\N{\fs14\b0}Odd prices for those garlands.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.17,0:25:30.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不只是奇怪  而是熟悉\N{\fs14\b0}Not just odd... familiar.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.85,0:25:35.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那本书上的  523  430  207\N{\fs14\b0}From the reference book, 523, 430, 207.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.35,0:25:36.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,代码信息\N{\fs14\b0}Coded message.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.76,0:25:37.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还在尝试破解它的信息\N{\fs14\b0}I'm trying to crack it as we speak.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.96,0:25:39.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看我们手里的那位朋友能不能帮上忙\N{\fs14\b0}Let's see if our friend in holding can help us.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.70,0:25:42.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会让梅菲尔派一队人去那家花店\N{\fs14\b0}I'll get Mayfair to send a team out to the flower shop.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.50,0:25:45.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会找到她的\N{\fs14\b0}We're gonna find her.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.59,0:25:47.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家花店的陈设\N{\fs14\b0}The display at the flower shop{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.64,0:25:49.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我们传递信息的方式\N{\fs14\b0}was our way of communicating{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.32,0:25:51.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以防图书馆的通信系统暴露了\N{\fs14\b0}in case the library system was compromised.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.93,0:25:54.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有什么没告诉我们的吗\N{\fs14\b0}You didn't think that was something we should know?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.59,0:25:57.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不乖乖合作对你没有任何好处\N{\fs14\b0}You're not making things easier on yourself.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.80,0:25:59.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些花代表了什么\N{\fs14\b0}What do the flowers mean?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.23,0:26:02.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我们目标的名字\N{\fs14\b0}They were our targets' names.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.01,0:26:04.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯特的目标是谁\N{\fs14\b0}So, who's Kate's target?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.42,0:26:06.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只有我自己目标的秘钥\N{\fs14\b0}I only had a key to decode my own.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.82,0:26:08.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是安全措施\N{\fs14\b0}It was a security measure{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.11,0:26:10.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以防我们有人被捕\N{\fs14\b0}in case any of us got compromised.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.27,0:26:12.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那好  把你的秘钥给我\N{\fs14\b0}Well, then, give me your key.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.43,0:26:13.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,俄国人动作很快\N{\fs14\b0}The Russians are moving fast.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.96,0:26:15.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们把花店烧了\N{\fs14\b0}They torched the flower shop.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.58,0:26:18.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等到我派出的探员赶到时\N{\fs14\b0}By the time the agents I sent out there arrived on the scene,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.23,0:26:19.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里已经燃起了大火\N{\fs14\b0}it was a four-alarm fire.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.79,0:26:21.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们想把店内电脑的数据清除\N{\fs14\b0}They tried to corrupt the data on the shop's computer,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.61,0:26:24.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我从他们的服务器中恢复了一些文件\N{\fs14\b0}but I was able to recover a partial file from their server.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.50,0:26:27.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天无畏号博物馆有场国防承包商博览会\N{\fs14\b0}There's a defense contractor expo at the Intrepid today.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.44,0:26:27.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎他们用她的照片伪造了入场证\N{\fs14\b0}Looks like they forged an entrance badge with her photo.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.47,0:26:30.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18\fn方正黑体简体}军事创新峰会\N凯特·威廉姆斯
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.44,0:26:31.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说  目标在这里\N{\fs14\b0}So that's where the target must be.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.80,0:26:32.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目标可能是任何人\N{\fs14\b0}That could be anyone.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.84,0:26:35.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种博览会能吸引来大批高层官员\N{\fs14\b0}Those kinds of expos attract a lot of high-ranking people.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.73,0:26:37.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我让手下检查一遍出席名单\N{\fs14\b0}I'll have my team go through the attendance list.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.74,0:26:38.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我继续研究花的密码\N{\fs14\b0}I'll keep working on the flower codes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.81,0:26:41.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  行动吧\N{\fs14\b0}All right, let's move.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.62,0:26:45.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帕特森  你查到什么了\N{\fs14\b0}Patterson, what do you got?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.56,0:26:48.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道目标是谁了  根据奥利维亚的秘钥\N{\fs14\b0}I figured out the target. So, based on Olivia's key,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.62,0:26:50.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我反向重建了花的密码\N{\fs14\b0}I reverse engineered the flower cipher{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.44,0:26:52.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是种改进的二进制密码\N{\fs14\b0}and it's a modified binary code.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.80,0:26:54.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我用破解软件\N{\fs14\b0}I ran every possible combination{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.51,0:26:55.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尝试了每种可能的组合\N{\fs14\b0}through my breakdown software,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.89,0:26:57.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得到了凯特目标的名字\N{\fs14\b0}and I got a name for Kate's target.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.59,0:27:00.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是康涅狄格州的史蒂夫·莱沃特参议员\N{\fs14\b0}It's Senator Steve Riewolt from Connecticut.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.43,0:27:03.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是参议院军事委员会的成员\N{\fs14\b0}He's a member of the Senate Armed Services Committee.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.92,0:27:04.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么是他\N{\fs14\b0}Why him?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.65,0:27:07.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他批准给乌克兰军方提供资金援助\N{\fs14\b0}He's behind the bill sending aid to the Ukrainian military.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.54,0:27:08.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他有带安保人员吗\N{\fs14\b0}Does he have a security detail?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.97,0:27:11.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他独自前往  我刚和他的华盛顿办公室通话\N{\fs14\b0}He's there alone, I just talked to his office in Washington,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.40,0:27:13.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,试过打他的手机  他没接\N{\fs14\b0}tried his cell, he's not picking up.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.76,0:27:14.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续打\N{\fs14\b0}Keep trying.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.67,0:27:16.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得尽快搜查完这艘船\N{\fs14\b0}We gotta canvas this ship as fast as possible.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.58,0:27:18.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每个人从不同的入口进\N{\fs14\b0}Everyone take a different entrance.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.81,0:27:59.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好像看见凯特了  她在二战展区\N{\fs14\b0}I think I see Kate... she's in the World War II exhibit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.27,0:28:10.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯特·威廉姆斯  联调局  举起手来\N{\fs14\b0}Kate Williams? FBI, put your hands up.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.92,0:28:13.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快\N{\fs14\b0}Now!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.26,0:28:17.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里德  把她丈夫抓起来  我去抓她\N{\fs14\b0}Reade, secure the husband. I got her, I got her!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.03,0:28:51.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威勒  你在哪\N{\fs14\b0}Weller, where are you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.44,0:28:52.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯特朝舰桥那边跑了\N{\fs14\b0}Kate's headed up to the bridge.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.82,0:28:54.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在追\N{\fs14\b0}I'm in pursuit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.01,0:28:56.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正朝你那边去\N{\fs14\b0}I'm headed your way.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.74,0:29:14.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看见凯特了\N{\fs14\b0}I got Kate!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.11,0:29:15.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她在飞行甲板上\N{\fs14\b0}She's on the flight deck{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.05,0:29:17.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往飞机旁边的楼梯跑\N{\fs14\b0}heading towards the stairs near the planes!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.95,0:29:36.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪边  船尾还是船头\N{\fs14\b0}Which way? Stern or bow!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.08,0:29:37.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,船头\N{\fs14\b0}Bow!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.76,0:31:13.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帕特森\N{\fs14\b0}Patterson.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.06,0:31:20.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帕特森  过来  来吧\N{\fs14\b0}Patterson, come on. Come on.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.09,0:31:40.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想谢谢你\N{\fs14\b0}I... I wanted to thank you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.48,0:31:43.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是我们没抓到她\N{\fs14\b0}If... if we didn't get her...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.16,0:31:47.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我\N{\fs14\b0}I...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.06,0:31:50.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs14\b0}Thank you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.08,0:31:53.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是我能做得多一些就好了\N{\fs14\b0}I wish that there was more that I could do.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.58,0:32:00.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以为如果我解决了这件事\N{\fs14\b0}I thought that if... if I... solved this,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.70,0:32:03.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到杀他的凶手\N{\fs14\b0}and if I found his killer,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.76,0:32:05.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就能感觉...\N{\fs14\b0}I would feel...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.81,0:32:12.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...\N{\fs14\b0}I...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.18,0:32:16.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我的感觉没变\N{\fs14\b0}But I feel the same.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.61,0:32:21.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是...空荡荡的\N{\fs14\b0}Just... empty.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.53,0:32:26.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,案件破了也没能改变任何事\N{\fs14\b0}Like solving this didn't change anything.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.80,0:32:30.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也有这种感觉吗\N{\fs14\b0}Is that what it's like for you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.48,0:32:34.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于那些纹身\N{\fs14\b0}With the tattoos?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.04,0:32:40.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太难受了\N{\fs14\b0}That's awful.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.54,0:32:47.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望我最近这几周能重新过一遍\N{\fs14\b0}I just wish I could relive the last few weeks.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.91,0:32:51.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不能那么想\N{\fs14\b0}You can't think like that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.18,0:32:53.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大卫说得对\N{\fs14\b0}I mean, David was right.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.74,0:32:57.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们...我们在一起很般配\N{\fs14\b0}We were... we were great together.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.99,0:33:01.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是太害怕了\N{\fs14\b0}And I was just scared.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.15,0:33:04.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不知道会发生这种事\N{\fs14\b0}You had no idea any of this was gonna happen.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.19,0:33:05.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我浪费了\N{\fs14\b0}I wasted{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.71,0:33:09.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么多精力  研究为什么行不通\N{\fs14\b0}so much energy on why it wouldn't work,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.18,0:33:11.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时我明明可以...\N{\fs14\b0}when I could've been...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.57,0:33:16.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱他\N{\fs14\b0}I loved him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.01,0:33:21.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...他当时就在我面前\N{\fs14\b0}And... and I... he was right in front of me,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.11,0:33:22.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我应该紧紧抱住他\N{\fs14\b0}and I should've just held onto him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.64,0:33:25.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但相反  我将他推开了\N{\fs14\b0}Instead, I just pushed him away.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.35,0:33:30.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如今他不在了\N{\fs14\b0}And now, he's gone.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.63,0:33:33.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来\N{\fs14\b0}Here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.42,0:33:39.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有你们\N{\fs14\b0}I don't know how I could've{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.49,0:33:42.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都不知道怎么熬过今天\N{\fs14\b0}gotten through today without all of you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.47,0:33:55.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都还好吗\N{\fs14\b0}Everything all right?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.13,0:33:57.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-是  -你的安保人员呢\N{\fs14\b0}- Yeah. - Where's your detail?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.08,0:33:59.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我溜出来了\N{\fs14\b0}Um, I snuck out.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.87,0:34:00.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这太不像话了\N{\fs14\b0}All right, that is crazy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.79,0:34:02.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们的工作就是贴身保护你\N{\fs14\b0}Their job is to be with you the whole time,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.12,0:34:04.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你到家时  保护你的安全\N{\fs14\b0}to look after you when you get home.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.01,0:34:06.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想见你\N{\fs14\b0}I just needed to see you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.18,0:34:08.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧\N{\fs14\b0}Is everything okay?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.56,0:34:22.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是...\N{\fs14\b0}I just, um...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.57,0:34:30.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想跟你独处一会儿\N{\fs14\b0}I wanted a moment that was just... us.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.06,0:34:43.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柯特叔叔\N{\fs14\b0}Uncle Kurt?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.10,0:34:49.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈说我可以帮你拿东西\N{\fs14\b0}Mom said I can help you with the groceries.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.42,0:34:51.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  你可以\N{\fs14\b0}Yeah, you... you can.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.11,0:34:53.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些...  你拿着吧\N{\fs14\b0}They're... they're... that's yours.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.81,0:34:55.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天见\N{\fs14\b0}See you tomorrow.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.22,0:34:56.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好\N{\fs14\b0}Okay.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.08,0:35:02.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是时候  真会挑时间\N{\fs14\b0}Great timing. Good timing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.07,0:35:32.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很抱歉又用这种方式跟你见面\N{\fs14\b0}Sorry we have to meet again like this.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.58,0:35:40.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是...\N{\fs14\b0}Just...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.60,0:35:47.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就明说现在的状况吧\N{\fs14\b0}so that there is clarity in, uh, in this situation,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.25,0:35:51.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,几个小时之后  你就会被送上飞机\N{\fs14\b0}you are hours away from being put on a plane{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.10,0:35:55.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关进一个只有我知道的小黑屋里\N{\fs14\b0}and sent down a dark hole that only I will know about.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.32,0:35:58.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个小黑屋的条件\N{\fs14\b0}How open you are in our brief time together{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.78,0:36:02.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全取决于你能不能坦白交代了\N{\fs14\b0}can radically affect how nice that hole is going to be.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.58,0:36:06.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以如果我是你  我就会...\N{\fs14\b0}So, if I were you, I would, um...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.17,0:36:09.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就会说实话\N{\fs14\b0}well, I'd tell the truth.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.98,0:36:11.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白吗\N{\fs14\b0}Yeah? Understood?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.78,0:36:15.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先要问  你是谁\N{\fs14\b0}So, first things first. Who are you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.06,0:36:17.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道我是谁\N{\fs14\b0}I don't know who I am.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.36,0:36:24.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你逼我动手的\N{\fs14\b0}Well, have it your way.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.99,0:36:43.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为谁效力\N{\fs14\b0}Who do you work for?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.22,0:36:45.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联调局\N{\fs14\b0}The FBI.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.19,0:36:48.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以不用受折磨的\N{\fs14\b0}You know, this could all be so easy.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.21,0:36:52.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很恐怖吧\N{\fs14\b0}It's horrible, right?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.76,0:36:55.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水呛进你的鼻腔和肺里\N{\fs14\b0}The water just burning in your nose and your lungs.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.66,0:36:58.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想呼吸  但却吸不到气\N{\fs14\b0}You want to breathe but you can't get any air.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.85,0:37:07.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说吧  你在哪纹的这些图案\N{\fs14\b0}So... wh-where did you get that fancy ink?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.30,0:37:07.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fs14\b0}I don't know.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.84,0:37:11.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问题是  我觉得你知道\N{\fs14\b0}See, here's the thing. I think you do.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.60,0:37:14.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再问你一次  你是谁\N{\fs14\b0}Again, who are you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.27,0:37:15.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fs14\b0}I don't know!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.63,0:37:17.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁把你送去联调局的\N{\fs14\b0}Well, who sent you to the FBI?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.51,0:37:18.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人\N{\fs14\b0}No one!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.86,0:37:31.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个项目叫"俄里翁"\N{\fs14\b0}The program's called Orion.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.57,0:37:34.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,俄里翁\N{\fs14\b0}Orion.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.23,0:37:38.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么\N{\fs14\b0}What did you say?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.45,0:37:43.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我  "俄里翁"是什么\N{\fs14\b0}Tell me... what's Orion?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.77,0:37:46.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在可不是由你来发问\N{\fs14\b0}See, that's not how this works.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.37,0:37:52.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来说说关于"俄里翁"  你都知道什么\N{\fs14\b0}You tell me what you know about Orion.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.69,0:37:56.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这会很疼的\N{\fs14\b0}See, this is gonna hurt.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.42,0:38:38.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不必那样做\N{\fs14\b0}You don't have to do that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.90,0:38:53.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简  是我\N{\fs14\b0}Jane, it's me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.53,0:38:56.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想知道  你有没有安全到家\N{\fs14\b0}I was just wondering if... if you got home safely.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.95,0:39:22.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧  我送你回家\N{\fs14\b0}Come on... I'm gonna take you home.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.99,0:39:27.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出门了  一小时后见\N{\fs14\b0}I'm headed out now, I'll see you in about an hour.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.33,0:39:28.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是\N{\fs14\b0}You too.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.21,0:39:39.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18\fn方正黑体简体}最后一次机会
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.26,0:39:49.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18\fn方正黑体简体}致 助理局长梅菲尔\N我在此辞去联调局的职务\N娜塔莎·萨帕塔
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.69,0:40:01.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么  你是谁\N{\fs14\b0}What is this? Who are you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.01,0:40:02.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么\N{\fs14\b0}What is that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.19,0:40:03.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你在看这段视频\N{\fs14\b0}If you're watching this,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.48,0:40:05.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,表明一切都在按计划进行中\N{\fs14\b0}the mission is going as planned.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.68,0:40:08.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以相信给你看视频的这个男人\N{\fs14\b0}You can trust the man who is showing you this video.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.01,0:40:11.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他叫奥斯卡  他是来帮你的\N{\fs14\b0}His name is Oscar, and he is here to help you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.88,0:40:17.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你很害怕  我知道你很困惑\N{\fs14\b0}I know that you're scared. I know that you're confused.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.55,0:40:21.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你想找出是谁对你做的这一切\N{\fs14\b0}And I know that you wanna find out who did this to you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.24,0:40:25.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,答案是你\N{\fs14\b0}The answer is you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.66,0:40:27.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纹身  抹去记忆\N{\fs14\b0}The tattoos, the memory wipe,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.36,0:40:29.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将你送到柯特·威勒那里\N{\fs14\b0}sending you to Kurt Weller.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.62,0:40:31.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是你自己的主意\N{\fs14\b0}This was all your idea.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.22,0:40:34.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你的计划\N{\fs14\b0}Your plan.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.31,0:40:37.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你对自己做了这一切\N{\fs14\b0}You did this to yourself.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.93,0:40:42.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你...才是幕后黑手\N{\fs14\b0}You... did this... to yourself.{\r}


